data.description:
Beautiful brick FOUR bedroom, two bath home in desirable Pike Road! The love and care given to this home is apparent. The split floor plan allows for privacy and a wonderful floor plan flow. This home is loaded with updates.  You can enjoy dinner in the formal dining room OR the eat-in kitchen  OR the breakfast bar, not to mention the covered backyard patio! The floor plan allows for oversized rooms and easy travel through the home. The three guest rooms and large guest bath are on one side of the home. On the opposite side, you can escape to the beautifully updated Master Suite-a haven waiting for you to enjoy every day! Every room has a large closet, modern fixtures and vinyl double paned windows. But that is not all. The kitchen has been updated to a light and airy, elegant and functional workspace with plenty of room, quality fixtures, a large pantry and direct access from the laundry/mud room. The oversized family room is ready for you to kick back and  start making memories. You can relax knowing the roof is only 5 years old. Most updates took place in the last 2 years. The back yard is fully privacy fenced. The front of the home boasts well manicured beds and tasteful yet low maintenance landscaping. This lovely home brings a ton of curb appeal to the quiet cul-de-sac it rests on. 
Guests, please use the provided shoe covers to protect carpet as you tour this home.
